  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "Project Rewrite was Penelope Centrella's program and this is the second thing that came out of it. One of a kind, reserved for special operations only, still active into the ilClan era. The Taser alone makes it worth studying carefully. Most commanders want to destroy what they fight. Whoever built this wanted the option to capture it intact instead. That tells you a lot about how Riley's Rangers operated.",
